OL,3,CText message costs nurse #45,000
OL,5,FITV News' Andy Bonner spoke to Pauline
OL,6,Fabout how one text message changed her
OL,7,Flife.
OL,9,FA critical care nurse who lost her
OL,10,Fentire pension pot of #45,000 after
OL,11,Fscammers sent her one text says she
OL,12,Fwas made to feel like "nothing".
OL,14,FPauline Padden, 61, was sent a message
OL,15,Fwhich promised a cash gift and a
OL,16,Fbigger pension if she moved her money.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
