OL,3,CText message costs nurse #45,000
OL,5,FBut instead, the critical care nurse,
OL,6,Fwho works at Alder Hey Children's
OL,7,FHospital in Liverpool, became one of
OL,8,F245 victims conned out of more than
OL,9,F#13.5million in pension savings.
OL,11,FShe is now warning others to be aware
OL,12,Fof the "callous" fraudsters, who saw
OL,13,Fher as "a number and name on a piece
OL,14,Fof paper" who she meant "nothing" to.
OL,16,FPauline said: "How stupid am I to let
OL,17,Fthat happen to me?
OL,19,F"I'll never get #45,000 together. I'm
OL,20,Fnot going to be working long enough to
OL,21,Fget that sort of money back.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
