OL,5,F"I'm 61 and I have to keep working."
OL,7,F"The scams are even more elaborate,
OL,8,Feven more clever, because the internet
OL,9,Fhas made it so," she added.
OL,11,F"I've worked hard for that money, and
OL,12,Fyou're just sitting there trying to
OL,13,Fthink of ways to get it off me."
OL,15,FPauline is now urging people to stop,
OL,16,Fthink and know the warning signs of
OL,17,Fscams, especially those who are in a
OL,18,Fvulnerable position like she was.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
