OL,5,F"My mum, this was her final three
OL,6,Fweeks and I just wanted to be with
OL,7,Fher," she said.
OL,9,F"But my finances at the time wouldn't
OL,10,Fallow me to do that, so I was in a bit
OL,11,Fof a quandary really.
OL,13,F"I desperately wanted to be with my
OL,14,Fmum, and I got this text through and
OL,15,Fthe text said, 'if you've got frozen
OL,16,Fpensions would you like to move them
OL,17,Fto a better investments and in return
OL,18,Ffor that receive a cash gift?'
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
