OL,3,CText message costs nurse #45,000
OL,5,F"So I thought, you know what? This
OL,6,Fsounds like this someone's been
OL,7,Flistening to my prayers. This is going
OL,8,Fto fix everything."
OL,10,FThe text told Pauline her money would
OL,11,Fbe invested in "exclusive properties"
OL,12,Fin the Caribbean which would then be
OL,13,Frented or sold off to give her a
OL,14,Freturn.
OL,16,FAs a reward for 'investing' she was
OL,17,Fgiven a 10% cash gift - but that money
OL,18,Fhad actually come from her own savings.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
