OL,5,FPauline says she was so distracted by
OL,6,Fher family situation, she did not even
OL,7,Fthink about the money until
OL,8,Finvestigators contacted her 18 months
OL,9,Flater to tell her the rest, more than
OL,10,F#40,000 had also been taken.
OL,12,F"They said, 'we're sorry, it's a scam.
OL,13,FYou've lost all your money'," she
OL,14,Fadded.
OL,16,F"I felt silly, stupid and still
OL,17,Fvulnerable, you know? How could I let
OL,18,Fthis happen to myself?"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
