OL,5,F"You've lost it now, what can you do?
OL,6,FIt's not like I could go to to the
OL,7,Fpolice because I willingly handed it
OL,8,Fover."
OL,10,FPauline is sharing her experience for
OL,11,FScams Awareness Week, which runs from
OL,12,F21 to 25 October.
OL,14,FShe said: "Look, I answered to a text,
OL,15,Fdon't. That's like doing deals on your
OL,16,Ffront doorstep, don't do that.
OL,18,F"Do your own due diligence, do your
OL,19,Fown research. If you want to move your
OL,20,Fpension or any investments that you
OL,21,Fhave, then let that come from you.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
