OL,5,FThe scammers, Alan Barratt and Susan
OL,6,FDalton, were jailed for a total of 10
OL,7,Fyears in 2022.
OL,9,FNone of the victims' money has been
OL,10,Frecovered, and Pauline is yet to see
OL,11,Fany compensation.
OL,13,FThe Pension Regulator (TPR) alongside
OL,14,FPension Scams Action Group (PSAG) says
OL,15,Fit is taking action to prevent more
OL,16,Fpeople falling victim.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
