OL,5,FGaucho Rasmussen, TPR's Executive
OL,6,FDirector of Regulatory Compliance,
OL,7,Fsaid: "Pauline's story starkly
OL,8,Fdemonstrates how ruthlessly scammers
OL,9,Fwill exploit victims' vulnerability to
OL,10,Fmake their ill-gotten gains.
OL,12,F"We urge pension savers to protect
OL,13,Fthemselves by knowing the warning
OL,14,Fsigns and how to avoid and report a
OL,15,Fscam or fraud. The message is clear -
OL,16,FStop, think and check who you are
OL,17,Fdealing with.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
